{
	"info": {
		"_postman_id": "a1b2c3d4-e5f6-7890-abcd-ef1234567890",
		"name": "User Upload API",
		"description": "API коллекция для проекта user-upload.\n\nАутентификация через OTP-верификацию по email и JWT-токены.\n\n**Флоу:**\n1. Register — регистрация и отправка OTP на email\n2. Verify OTP — подтверждение email кодом из письма\n3. Login — получение JWT-токена\n4. Upload Image — загрузка изображения (требуется JWT)\n5. List Images — список изображений с фильтрами\n6. Delete Image — удаление изображения\n\n**Rate Limit:** 5 запросов в минуту на auth-эндпоинты.",
		"schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
	},
	"variable": [
		{
			"key": "base_url",
			"value": "http://localhost:8000",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "token",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "user_email",
			"value": "test@example.com",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "user_password",
			"value": "password123",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "user_name",
			"value": "Test User",
			"type": "string"
		},
		{
			"key": "image_id",
			"value": "",
			"type": "string"
		}
	],
	"item": [
		{
			"name": "Auth",
			"description": "Эндпоинты аутентификации: регистрация, OTP-верификация, логин.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Register",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has user_id and resend', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('user_id');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('resend');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"name\": \"{{user_name}}\",\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\",\n    \"password_confirmation\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/register",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "register"]
						},
						"description": "Регистрация нового пользователя.\n\nОтправляет 6-значный OTP-код на указанный email. Код действителен 5 минут.\n\n**Валидация:**\n- `name` — обязательно, 2–255 символов\n- `email` — обязательно, валидный email\n- `password` — обязательно, 8–128 символов, требуется подтверждение\n\n**Ошибки:**\n- `409` — пользователь уже верифицирован"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "201 Created",
							"status": "Created",
							"code": 201,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 201,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Created\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"resend\": 60\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "409 Conflict — User Already Exists",
							"status": "Conflict",
							"code": 409,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 409,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Conflict\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"message\": \"User already exists.\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "422 Validation Error",
							"status": "Unprocessable Entity",
							"code": 422,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"The name field is required.\",\n    \"errors\": {\n        \"name\": [\"The name field is required.\"],\n        \"email\": [\"The email field is required.\"],\n        \"password\": [\"The password field is required.\"]\n    }\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Verify OTP",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has user data', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('name');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('email');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n    \"code\": 123456\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/verify-otp",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "verify-otp"]
						},
						"description": "Верификация email с помощью OTP-кода.\n\nПосле успешной регистрации пользователь получает 6-значный код на email. Код нужно отправить в этот эндпоинт.\n\n**Валидация:**\n- `email` — обязательно, валидный email\n- `code` — обязательно, 6-значное целое число\n\n**Ошибки:**\n- `404` — пользователь не найден\n- `422` — неверный или истёкший OTP-код"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK — User Verified",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Ok\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"name\": \"Test User\",\n        \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n        \"images_count\": 0,\n        \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:00:00+00:00\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "404 User Not Found",
							"status": "Not Found",
							"code": 404,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"User not found\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "422 Invalid OTP",
							"status": "Unprocessable Entity",
							"code": 422,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Invalid or expired OTP code\"\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Login",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has user and token', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('user');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('token');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data.user).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data.user).to.have.property('name');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data.user).to.have.property('email');",
									"});",
									"",
									"// Auto-save token to collection variable",
									"if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('token', jsonData.data.token);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Content-Type",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "raw",
							"raw": "{\n    \"email\": \"{{user_email}}\",\n    \"password\": \"{{user_password}}\"\n}"
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/auth/login",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "auth", "login"]
						},
						"description": "Аутентификация пользователя и получение JWT-токена.\n\nПользователь должен быть верифицирован (пройти OTP-верификацию).\n\nПри успешном логине токен автоматически сохраняется в переменную `{{token}}`.\n\n**Валидация:**\n- `email` — обязательно, валидный email\n- `password` — обязательно, строка\n\n**Ошибки:**\n- `401` — неверные учётные данные\n- `403` — email не верифицирован"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK — Login Success",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Ok\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"user\": {\n            \"id\": 1,\n            \"name\": \"Test User\",\n            \"email\": \"test@example.com\",\n            \"images_count\": 0,\n            \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:00:00+00:00\"\n        },\n        \"token\": \"eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9...\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "401 Unauthorized",
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Invalid credentials\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "403 Forbidden — Not Verified",
							"status": "Forbidden",
							"code": 403,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Email is not verified\"\n}"
						}
					]
				}
			]
		},
		{
			"name": "Images",
			"description": "Управление изображениями. Все эндпоинты требуют JWT-токен в заголовке Authorization.",
			"item": [
				{
					"name": "Upload Image",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 201', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has image data', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('original_name');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('mime_type');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('size');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('url');",
									"});",
									"",
									"// Auto-save image_id for delete request",
									"if (pm.response.code === 201) {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.collectionVariables.set('image_id', jsonData.data.id);",
									"}"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "POST",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							}
						],
						"body": {
							"mode": "formdata",
							"formdata": [
								{
									"key": "image",
									"type": "file",
									"src": "",
									"description": "JPEG или PNG, макс. 5 MB"
								}
							]
						},
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/images/upload",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "images", "upload"]
						},
						"description": "Загрузка изображения. Требуется JWT-токен.\n\nФайл отправляется как `multipart/form-data`.\n\nПосле загрузки автоматически запускается фоновая компрессия.\n\n**Валидация:**\n- `image` — обязательно, файл, только JPEG/PNG, макс. 5 MB\n\n**Ошибки:**\n- `401` — не авторизован\n- `422` — ошибка валидации (формат, размер)"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "201 Created",
							"status": "Created",
							"code": 201,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 201,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Created\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"original_name\": \"photo.jpg\",\n        \"mime_type\": \"image/jpeg\",\n        \"size\": 245760,\n        \"is_compressed\": false,\n        \"url\": \"http://localhost:8000/storage/images/ab/cd/abc123.jpg\",\n        \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:30:00+00:00\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "401 Unauthorized",
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Unauthenticated.\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "422 Validation Error",
							"status": "Unprocessable Entity",
							"code": 422,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Only JPEG and PNG formats are allowed.\",\n    \"errors\": {\n        \"image\": [\"Only JPEG and PNG formats are allowed.\"]\n    }\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "List Images",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has pagination and list', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('pagination');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('list');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data.pagination).to.have.property('current');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data.pagination).to.have.property('totalItem');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/images?per_page=20&sort_by=created_at&sort_direction=desc",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "images"],
							"query": [
								{
									"key": "per_page",
									"value": "20",
									"description": "Кол-во на страницу (по умолчанию 20)"
								},
								{
									"key": "sort_by",
									"value": "created_at",
									"description": "Сортировка: created_at, original_name, size"
								},
								{
									"key": "sort_direction",
									"value": "desc",
									"description": "Направление: asc или desc"
								},
								{
									"key": "original_name",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Фильтр по имени файла (частичное совпадение)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "mime_type",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Фильтр по MIME-типу: image/jpeg, image/png",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "date_from",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Дата от (YYYY-MM-DD)",
									"disabled": true
								},
								{
									"key": "date_to",
									"value": "",
									"description": "Дата до (YYYY-MM-DD)",
									"disabled": true
								}
							]
						},
						"description": "Список изображений текущего пользователя с пагинацией и фильтрами.\n\nТребуется JWT-токен.\n\n**Query-параметры (все необязательные):**\n- `per_page` — кол-во на страницу (по умолчанию 20)\n- `sort_by` — поле сортировки: `created_at`, `original_name`, `size`\n- `sort_direction` — `asc` или `desc` (по умолчанию `desc`)\n- `original_name` — фильтр по имени (частичное совпадение)\n- `mime_type` — фильтр по MIME-типу (`image/jpeg`, `image/png`)\n- `date_from` — дата от (YYYY-MM-DD)\n- `date_to` — дата до (YYYY-MM-DD)"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK — Image List",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Ok\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"pagination\": {\n            \"current\": 1,\n            \"previous\": 0,\n            \"next\": 2,\n            \"perPage\": 20,\n            \"totalPage\": 3,\n            \"totalItem\": 47\n        },\n        \"list\": [\n            {\n                \"id\": 1,\n                \"original_name\": \"photo.jpg\",\n                \"mime_type\": \"image/jpeg\",\n                \"size\": 245760,\n                \"is_compressed\": true,\n                \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:30:00+00:00\"\n            },\n            {\n                \"id\": 2,\n                \"original_name\": \"screenshot.png\",\n                \"mime_type\": \"image/png\",\n                \"size\": 1048576,\n                \"is_compressed\": false,\n                \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:25:00+00:00\"\n            }\n        ]\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "401 Unauthorized",
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Unauthenticated.\"\n}"
						}
					]
				},
				{
					"name": "Get Image",
					"event": [
						{
							"listen": "test",
							"script": {
								"exec": [
									"pm.test('Status code is 200', function () {",
									"    pm.response.to.have.status(200);",
									"});",
									"",
									"pm.test('Response has image data', function () {",
									"    var jsonData = pm.response.json();",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('id');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('original_name');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('mime_type');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('size');",
									"    pm.expect(jsonData.data).to.have.property('url');",
									"});"
								],
								"type": "text/javascript"
							}
						}
					],
					"request": {
						"method": "GET",
						"header": [
							{
								"key": "Accept",
								"value": "application/json"
							},
							{
								"key": "Authorization",
								"value": "Bearer {{token}}"
							}
						],
						"url": {
							"raw": "{{base_url}}/api/images/{{image_id}}",
							"host": ["{{base_url}}"],
							"path": ["api", "images", "{{image_id}}"]
						},
						"description": "Получение конкретного изображения по ID. Требуется JWT-токен.\n\nМожно получить только свои изображения.\n\n**Ошибки:**\n- `401` — не авторизован\n- `403` — изображение принадлежит другому пользователю\n- `404` — изображение не найдено"
					},
					"response": [
						{
							"name": "200 OK",
							"status": "OK",
							"code": 200,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 200,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Ok\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"id\": 1,\n        \"original_name\": \"photo.jpg\",\n        \"mime_type\": \"image/jpeg\",\n        \"size\": 245760,\n        \"is_compressed\": true,\n        \"url\": \"http://localhost:8000/storage/images/ab/cd/abc123.jpg\",\n        \"created_at\": \"2026-03-15T12:30:00+00:00\"\n    }\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "401 Unauthorized",
							"status": "Unauthorized",
							"code": 401,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"message\": \"Unauthenticated.\"\n}"
						},
						{
							"name": "403 Forbidden",
							"status": "Forbidden",
							"code": 403,
							"header": [
								{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}
							],
							"body": "{\n    \"statusCode\": 403,\n    \"statusDescription\": \"Forbidden\",\n    \"data\": {\n        \"message\": \"Forbidden\"\n    }\n}"
